The paper focuses on exploring interactions with a recommendation-oriented voice-controlled TV system, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
